    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-12-23T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-12-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="641"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d641">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">693.003/535: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Arnold</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-12-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 23, 1918</hi>.</date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received December 24, 8.58 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Tariff Commissions sessions concluded. Delegates unanimously agreed recommending
                    to respective Governments adoption Commission’s proposed revised tariff.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Arnold</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
